Class ScanLiteralAssembler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.plasma.query.visitor.DefaultQueryVisitor
      • org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan.ScanLiteralAssembler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.plasma.query.visitor.QueryVisitor

    public class ScanLiteralAssembler
extends org.plasma.query.visitor.DefaultQueryVisitor
    Assembles the set of data "flavor" and data type specific scan literals used to construct composite partial row (start/stop) key pair.

    0.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
